    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. Combined uncertainty for the primary QoI is characterised via structured UQ for the RH index and pressure rise comparisons. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU. Assessment accepted by the credibility review board.",
